@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1

### 3.1 Generar Póliza - Empleado 1, Laptop (10 unidades)
POST {{baseUrl}}/polizas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idEmpleado": 1,
  "sku": "LAPTOP-DELL-001",
  "cantidad": 1
}

